      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Louis Zulli</b>\n</p><p><b>Louis Philip Zulli</b>,<br />\nan American mathematician and associate professor at department of mathematics, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lafayette_College\">Lafayette College</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Easton,_Pennsylvania\">Easton, Pennsylvania</a>, with special interests in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knot_theory\">knot theory</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Low-dimensional_topology\">low-dimensional topology</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linear_algebra\">linear algebra</a> over <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GF%282%29\">Z/2Z</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe holds a Ph.D. from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cornell_University\">Cornell University</a> in 1993 under <a href=\"/Mathematician#AllenHatcher\" title=\"Mathematician\">Allen Hatcher</a>, where he introduced a way to calculate the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jones_polynomial\">Jones polynomial</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> of a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knot_%28mathematics%29\">knot</a> using a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symmetric_matrix\">symmetric matrix</a>, called the trip matrix, over Z/2Z  \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \nHis none professional interests include chess and chess programming, in particular <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source engines</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Apple&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Apple (page does not exist)\">Apple</a> <a href=\"/Macintosh\" title=\"Macintosh\">Macintosh</a> such as <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a> and <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">parallel search</a> topics, and writing his own engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=Kirby&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kirby (page does not exist)\">Kirby</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1993_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1993 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1993_...\">1993 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1993 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=920418\">A Matrix for Computing the Jones Polynomial of a Knot</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#AllenHatcher\" title=\"Mathematician\">Allen Hatcher</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cornell_University\">Cornell University</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/238852126_A_matrix_for_computing_the_Jones_polynomial_of_a_knot\">A Matrix for Computing the Jones Polynomial of a Knot</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Topology_%28journal%29\">Topology</a>, Vol. 34, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>1997</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/266451201_The_Rank_of_the_Trip_Matrix_of_a_Positive_Knot_Diagram\">The Rank of the Trip Matrix of a Positive Knot Diagram</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Knot_Theory_and_Its_Ramifications\">Journal of Knot Theory and Its Ramifications</a>, Vol. 6, No. 2</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.jstor.org/stable/2690781?seq=1#page_scan_tab_contents\">The Incredibly Knotty Checkerboard Challenge</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematics_Magazine\">Mathematics Magazine</a>, Vol. 71, No. 5 <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.ams.org/journals/proc/2002-130-07/S0002-9939-01-06320-1/\">A prime curve is determined by its VF-matrix</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proceedings_of_the_American_Mathematical_Society\">Proceedings of the American Mathematical Society</a>, Vol 130, No. 7</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/268610066_A_matrix_invariant_of_curves_in_S_2\">A Matrix Invariant of Curves in S2</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Knot_Theory_and_Its_Ramifications\">Journal of Knot Theory and Its Ramifications</a>, Vol. 11, No. 5</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Shtylla:Blerta\">Blerta Shtylla</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.worldscientific.com/doi/abs/10.1142/S0218216506004294\">An Extension of the Jones Polynomial of Classical Knots</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Knot_Theory_and_Its_Ramifications\">Journal of Knot Theory and Its Ramifications</a>, Vol. 15, No. 1, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.lafayette.edu/~zullil/JonesExt.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/t/Traldi:Lorenzo\">Lorenzo Traldi</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/1771664_A_bracket_polynomial_for_graphs_I\">A bracket polynomial for graphs</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Journal_of_Knot_Theory_and_Its_Ramifications\">Journal of Knot Theory and Its Ramifications</a>,, Vol. 18, No. 12, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://arxiv.org/abs/0808.3392v2\">arXiv:0808.3392v2</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Shtylla:Blerta\">Blerta Shtylla</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/t/Traldi:Lorenzo\">Lorenzo Traldi</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/1765714_On_the_realization_of_double_occurrence_words\">On the Realization of Double Occurrence Words</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Discrete_Mathematics_%28journal%29\">Discrete Mathematics</a>, Vol. 309, No. 6, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://arxiv.org/abs/0709.2933\">arXiv:0709.2933</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/t/Traldi:Lorenzo\">Lorenzo Traldi</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0166864109003277?via%3Dihub\">Topological realizations of ortho-projection graphs</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Topology_and_Its_Applications\">Topology and its Applications</a>, Vol. 156, No. 15</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=17478\">Crafty 21.6</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 30, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27116\">Crafty-Rybka draw in CCT Round 6</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 22, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/CCT11\" title=\"CCT11\">CCT11</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31388\">Stockfish-1.6.2 Benchmarks for 1 to 8 Threads</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 31, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31767\">Another Crafty-23.1 Nehalem scaling problem</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 16, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32750\">Using the GPU</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2010 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=33705\">Stockfish-1.7.0 Hyper-threading Detection</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 09, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37468\">Stockfish \"Use Sleeping Threads\" Test</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42059\">Stockfish benchmark</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 19, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47106\">Feeling like Morphy</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Kirby&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Kirby (page does not exist)\">Kirby</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47162\">Quiescent search, and side to move is in check</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 08, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49679\">Is there an engine written in Go?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 12, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Go_(Programming_Language)\" title=\"Go (Programming Language)\">Go (Programming Language)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51291\">Disabling Null Move Pruning in Stockfish</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sourceforge.net/p/chessx/mailman/message/32443500/\">Limit time that engines may use for analysis</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/ChessX\" title=\"ChessX\">ChessX</a> / Mailing Lists, June 10, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52781\">Stockfish Status Report</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 27, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53120\">Is 79 maximal?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 29, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Forsyth-Edwards_Notation\" title=\"Forsyth-Edwards Notation\">Forsyth-Edwards Notation</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54636\">USB 3 Storage for Syzygy WDL files</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 13, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55352\">Stockfish with 16 threads - big news?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2015</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55368\">Explanation for non-expert?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 16, 2015</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66462\">Cfish 9 is OUT!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 31, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/CFish\" title=\"CFish\">CFish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67000\">Why was Lyudmil banned?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 02, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71027\">Some NUMA data for Stockfish-dev and Cfish-dev</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/NUMA\" title=\"NUMA\">NUMA</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/CFish\" title=\"CFish\">CFish</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://math.lafayette.edu/people/louis-zulli/\">Home Page of Louis Zulli</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=23415\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Louis Zulli</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Zulli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://math.lafayette.edu/people/louis-zulli/\">Louis Zulli · Math · Lafayette College</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Mathematician#LouisKauffman\" title=\"Mathematician\">Louis Kauffman</a> and <a href=\"/Mathematician#VaughanJones\" title=\"Mathematician\">Vaughan Jones</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a> (<b>1993</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=920418\">A Matrix for Computing the Jones Polynomial of a Knot</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#AllenHatcher\" title=\"Mathematician\">Allen Hatcher</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cornell_University\">Cornell University</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47106\">Feeling like Morphy</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2013</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52697&amp;start=9\">Thanks</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Louis Zulli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 20, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Louis_Zulli\">